 # SSL/TLS Management Guide

## Overview

All homelab services use SSL/TLS encryption with certificates issued by FreeIPA Certificate Authority. This provides encrypted connections and centralized certificate management.

## Architecture

SSL Termination at Nginx: - External clients connect via HTTPS (encrypted) - Nginx terminates SSL and decrypts traffic - Backend services communicate via HTTP on trusted Docker network - All HTTP requests automatically redirect to HTTPS

Certificate Authority: - FreeIPA configured as internal Certificate Authority - Issues certificates for all services - Centralized trust chain management

